{
  "stem": "24346.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have a dear friend there, that he can do for me-- because my cousin worked with the girls in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they also got enough food-- there wasn't a problem after the war, so much, the food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I left there for-- for Zeilsheim.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sure enough, I came to the camp and I asked, where's Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Weiner live?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They showed me, I knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I came-- oh, Henrik, happy we meet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, well, look, I would like you to-- you should register me in this camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, yes, I went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't work out there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I told him the story with the AK, they're shooting machine-guns on the street, Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, it's not for me and I came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you want to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I don't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Give me any job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I should get an extra ration, we should have enough-- he said, do you want to join the police?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They'll train you here, we have, you know, people who can-- I said, I don't care.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, we'll make you a policeman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, assign me an apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me an apartment, they assigned an apartment then gave me the police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the police had already-- beside what we get, the rations from the camp-- you know, because we used to get rations there, food.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't a starvation ration-- a starvation ration-- we got already enough food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Beside that, we used to have an open casino for the police that we used to go and they eat breakfast, lunch, and dinner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had double food, so it was already fine, thanks to Volvek Weiner.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
